WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:02:49.528
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:02:49.529 --> 00:02:56.893
Well, good evening, family. Let's see here. Braden has some news. There's all kinds of stuff going on in the world today.

00:02:56.894 --> 00:03:02.952
President Trump is upset, and should be, for the rigging of elections in California.

00:03:02.953 --> 00:03:09.618
We know that there's a red wave by the spirit of God and what the Lord has showed us, but they're going to try to steal the election.

00:03:09.619 --> 00:03:16.955
And I know, just like they did with Sleepy Joe and how they tried to do it last time, but it was too big to rig.

00:03:16.956 --> 00:03:20.737
We already know what they're doing in certain counties and certain states.

00:03:20.738 --> 00:03:29.465
Now, I know here we are—California, they still don't have all the vote count. We don't have it all counted. It's just this little area.

00:03:29.466 --> 00:03:34.399
We got to wait till the votes come in, and now it's all going towards Democrats.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:39.528
And so, we know what they're doing. And so does the government, I'm sure.

00:03:39.529 --> 00:03:44.125
President Trump, I know he has common sense; he knows what they're doing because they did it to him.

00:03:44.126 --> 00:03:52.817
So, we pray for Spencer Pratt. We pray for the governor's race and all the things that are taking place in California.

00:03:52.818 --> 00:04:00.101
I believe that we're about to see one of the greatest revivals the world has ever seen before, and we're going to see it in California.

00:04:00.102 --> 00:04:05.160
God's not done with California. The greater the blue, the greater the revival.

00:04:05.161 --> 00:04:08.155
That's what I keep saying. The greater the blue, the greater the revival.

00:04:08.156 --> 00:04:13.129
That's what I heard when I was praying. He said, 'Brandon, I...'He's not freaking out about it.

00:04:13.130 --> 00:04:21.920
'We're going to expose this ahead of time so it doesn't go into 2028. We don't want this going into 2028.

00:04:21.921 --> 00:04:29.865
We want the head of the snake to be cut off right now.'And what a way to find it out before even November!

00:04:29.866 --> 00:04:39.471
You know, this is before the prelude of November to vote them all in. So, we got to fix this stuff before, and we know it's there.

00:04:39.472 --> 00:04:44.465
So, we're going to go ahead now in the name of Jesus and find out where all this fraud is going on.

00:04:44.466 --> 00:04:51.165
And we know it's in Minnesota; we know it's in a lot of places. And so, what a way to find it out, huh?

00:04:51.166 --> 00:04:54.990
So, we're going to keep praying, and we're going to keep believing God.

00:04:54.991 --> 00:05:00.036
California is not done. I believe Malibu is going to get a great shaking.

00:05:00.037 --> 00:05:07.599
And like I said, I've had people email me and they say, 'Hey, Brandon, this is why we believe it's Malibu, and it's a bad commute.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:15.514
There's, you know, all kinds of traffic and all this other stuff.'But you know, I've never been to Malibu, but it sounds pretty.

00:05:15.515 --> 00:05:21.562
And I thought, 'Well, what the Lord said: a major shaking's coming. A major shaking's coming.

00:05:21.563 --> 00:05:36.772
There will be signs and wonders following.'I'm believing, even with Mel Gibson's movie, with the movie coming out next year, this new Passion of the Christ 2, that we're going to see a great harvest of souls come from the Passion of the Christ 2.

00:05:36.773 --> 00:05:46.149
And so, I'm just anticipating now. Please forgive me... Pastor Maldonado, right? Yeah, yes.

00:05:46.150 --> 00:05:56.833
Text me, not email me, and said, 'Hey, Brandon, we had over two and a half million people show up to the meeting in Brazil.

00:05:56.834 --> 00:06:04.719
Thank you for praying.'Now, here's the awesome part. He said, 'We had a million salvations.

00:06:04.720 --> 00:06:13.076
1 million people in Brazil gave their heart to Jesus Christ this weekend, Friday.

00:06:13.077 --> 00:06:22.399
A million people.'This is the meeting. This is Pastor Maldonado.

00:06:22.400 --> 00:06:27.275
They had King Jesus. Look at all the people there. They were preaching to the people.

00:06:27.276 --> 00:06:42.610
Millions showed up, and the police had so much security and so much watching over the people as they were having the service.

00:06:42.611 --> 00:06:47.956
This is him. He said there were lots of people got healed by the power of God.

00:06:47.957 --> 00:07:00.392
Eyes were opened, deaf ears. The lame were walking. They saw miracles in Brazil. Now, this is awesome. He said to me, 'Keep praying.

00:07:00.393 --> 00:07:18.726
The man that has the beard that we prophesied over, and I saw about the corruption concerning the cartel and trying to sway this man and blackmail this man in the days ahead, he is a born-again believer.'Pastor Maldonado said, 'I know him.

00:07:18.727 --> 00:07:27.171
I know him. He invited me to hold crusades in Colombia in the weeks ahead if he wins the election.

00:07:27.172 --> 00:08:02.055
And he said he's invited me to hold major Holy Ghost meetings in an arena there, and he said that he would accommodate us in any way possible to hold meetings for salvations and healings and miracles in Colombia.'So the Lord said to us, if you go back to it, 'I will reach South America in the days ahead.'And he said, 'Brandon, there's so many people here that watch you on your Portuguese channel and your Spanish channel, and they know you.

00:08:02.056 --> 00:08:13.831
I've brought you up, and there's a lot of people that know you and they watch you.'So, it's exciting that we're reaching the nations for Jesus here at our little prayer channel.

00:08:13.832 --> 00:08:19.116
You know, I believe God that it's going to keep growing, but we're reaching the nations for Jesus.

00:08:19.117 --> 00:08:35.950
And Pastor said over there, 'This is what is happening in South America, and you prophesied this.'Now, we're going to believe God for Cuba, and we're going to believe God for the open doors for the harvest.

00:08:35.951 --> 00:08:41.249
This is the most important thing of all the things that we ever talk about on this channel.

00:08:41.250 --> 00:08:48.319
All the things that we see that the Lord leads us to pray over and all the things that we believe we avert.

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:57.875
The most important thing that you need to know is do you know Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior? We are coming to the end of the end here.

00:08:57.876 --> 00:09:05.696
We're at the last of the last days, and it's exciting to see that over a million people gave their heart to Jesus Christ this weekend.

00:09:05.697 --> 00:09:10.178
Do you have any more clips of that, of him? Yeah, of the crowd.

00:09:10.179 --> 00:09:15.611
I get excited about the people. Yes. I don't know how to fast forward on this.

00:09:15.612 --> 00:09:26.498
Look at all those people. Yeah. Do you all see that? They're all coming to hear about Jesus. It's not about us; it's about Jesus.

00:09:26.499 --> 00:09:34.158
And it's wonderful to see miracles, signs, and wonders follow those that believe, and that the people are lining up outside.

00:09:34.159 --> 00:09:46.719
There's standing room only out there. Look at that! Over two and a half million people all throughout the whole city.

00:09:46.720 --> 00:09:52.931
1 million salvations. And he told me—he texted me right after he got off the platform, and he said, 'Thank you for praying for us.

00:09:52.932 --> 00:09:58.843
Thank you.'And it's because of people like you. Many hands make light work. We are part of that.

00:09:58.844 --> 00:10:06.958
We prayed for those souls; we prayed for the salvations; we prayed for the healings; we prayed for manifestations of the glory of God in these last days.

00:10:06.959 --> 00:10:13.699
And I'm expecting that this is just the beginning because the Lord said he was going to use this man in the Latino community.

00:10:13.700 --> 00:10:29.999
He told me, 'I'm going to use him, and I'm going to pour out my spirit on these meetings, and I'm going to bring in lots of people, and he'll be like a modern-day Billy Graham in South America to the Latinos.'And so, it's happening.

00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:38.799
You see it? As far as you can see, look at that. They're lined down the street.

00:10:38.800 --> 00:10:41.714
So, we were excited about it. My family and I were rejoicing.

00:10:41.715 --> 00:10:49.999
We were a part, praying into that and praying over the people giving their hearts to Jesus Christ.

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:55.642
You should be excited, too. Jesus Christ is coming, and this is just the beginning.

00:10:55.643 --> 00:11:04.962
This is going to happen in Europe, this is going to happen in South Africa, it's going to happen in Asia—all over the planet.

00:11:04.963 --> 00:11:13.714
We're about to see the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen before, and I'm anticipating what God is going to do through you.

00:11:13.715 --> 00:11:20.731
It's not just about Brandon. It's not about him. It's about all hands on deck.

00:11:20.732 --> 00:11:27.759
If you will just say yes to Jesus, Jesus will use you. Just say, 'God, here am I.

00:11:27.760 --> 00:11:32.013
Use me.'And you'll have a park full of people when the glory shows up.

00:11:32.014 --> 00:11:37.079
We're reading 'Daughters of Destiny'by Kathryn Kuhlman's book.

00:11:37.080 --> 00:11:41.952
Billy recommended it, and he said, 'Brandon, this is a good book.'We started reading that.

00:11:41.953 --> 00:11:47.939
I haven't been able to have Diana put it down. She reads it to me. I said, "Read it again. Read the page again.

00:11:47.940 --> 00:11:54.684
I need this about the persecution, what she went through."And the book is just wow.

00:11:54.685 --> 00:12:07.034
I don't know, I guess it just echoes inside of me because of what we've went through this last year, real heavy, and just what God has called us and what He's told us we're going to do.

00:12:07.035 --> 00:12:13.836
And it's exciting to see the beginnings of somebody, even whenever you think you derail yourself.

00:12:13.837 --> 00:12:17.996
And the Lord said, "Brandon, you're not big enough to derail yourself.

00:12:17.997 --> 00:12:22.961
You're not big enough."He goes, "The footsteps of the righteous are ordered of the Lord.

00:12:22.962 --> 00:12:28.985
No matter what the devil means for bad, I'll turn it around for good in your favor if you're trusting in me.

00:12:28.986 --> 00:12:37.328
Trust confidently in me, Brandon, and I will give you the desires of your heart. I will give you the nations. I'll do whatever.

00:12:37.329 --> 00:12:49.782
Your God is as big as your faith will allow Him to be."God is as big as your faith will allow Him to be.

00:12:49.783 --> 00:12:58.078
Not my faith. Your faith. Without faith, it is impossible to please Him.

00:12:58.079 --> 00:13:05.233
So we come to God knowing that He is and that He is a rewarder of those that diligently seek Him.

00:13:05.234 --> 00:13:21.923
And if you're diligently seeking Him, the Bible says in Matthew 5:8—I believe it's 8:5 or 5:8—He said, "Blessed are the pure in heart, for they will see God."Blessed are the pure in heart.

00:13:21.924 --> 00:13:30.832
That was Jesus that said that. Blessed are the pure in heart, for they will see the Lord. They will see God.

00:13:30.833 --> 00:13:37.759
And I believe there's a lot of pure in heart people here in the middle of a Sunday night, when you could be doing anything else other than praying.

00:13:37.760 --> 00:13:42.569
You're here tonight because you have hunger. You're stirred inside of yourself.

00:13:42.570 --> 00:13:56.159
It's 5:8. "Blessed are the pure in heart, for they shall see God."Matthew 5:8. I sometimes flip numbers. So, but it's not 8:5, it's 5:8.

00:13:56.160 --> 00:14:11.999
Praise the Lord, because I believe that the eyes of the Lord are going to and fro throughout the whole earth, looking for a heart who's perfect toward Him, so He can show Himself strong.

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:17.777
He can make His covenant strong on their behalf. Look, blessed are the pure in heart.

00:14:17.778 --> 00:14:22.666
For the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth, looking for a heart.

00:14:22.667 --> 00:14:29.052
Pure in heart. He's looking for hearts. Blessed are the pure in heart.

00:14:29.053 --> 00:14:34.610
For the eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth, looking for a heart who's perfect toward Him.

00:14:34.611 --> 00:14:40.559
Who are the pure? Who are the ones that He's falling on? How do His eyes stop on you?

00:14:40.560 --> 00:14:45.064
Blessed are the pure in heart, for they'll see God, for He's looking.

00:14:45.065 --> 00:14:51.278
He's looking for a heart who's perfect toward Him. He's looking for the pure in heart.

00:14:51.279 --> 00:14:58.398
God's looking for you. God's looking for me. He's looking to see, "Can I use them?

00:14:58.399 --> 00:15:07.179
Will they just say yes in these last days? Will they just say yes?"The harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:15:07.180 --> 00:15:14.855
Will you help Him bring in the harvest? As you see Maldonado, he's preaching the gospel in front of millions of people.

00:15:14.856 --> 00:15:25.619
One man, but he said yes. And millions of people—one million souls—gave their heart to Jesus Christ this weekend.

00:15:25.620 --> 00:15:34.305
And I'm excited about that. I just go, "Man, praise the Lord."Just say, "Yes, Lord.

00:15:34.306 --> 00:15:41.418
Here am I."Do you understand? We've got to get out of our small mentality of thinking.

00:15:41.419 --> 00:15:47.920
I see that and I go, "My goodness, Lord, if you can use him, you'll use me. If you can use her, you'll use me.

00:15:47.921 --> 00:15:52.990
If you could use Kathryn Kuhlman and the things I was reading about in the book, you can use me.

00:15:52.991 --> 00:15:59.439
If you can use Billy Burke, you can use me. If you can use so-and-so, you can use me.

00:15:59.440 --> 00:16:04.280
Blessed are the pure in heart, for they will see God."Does that make sense?

00:16:04.281 --> 00:16:25.633
I try to encourage you to stop thinking so small about yourself, because God will use anybody who would just say—remember the man in the Bible, he said, "I am of unclean lips, Lord."But the angel took the coal from the altar and put it on his lips and purified him.

00:16:25.634 --> 00:16:38.958
It was a prophet. Where's that scripture at, Braden? He took the coal from the altar, and the angel put it on his lips.

00:16:38.959 --> 00:16:55.278
He said, "I'm a man of unclean lips."Isaiah. Isaiah. People in that comment section will tell you, if God will use them, He will use you.

00:16:55.279 --> 00:17:07.889
I know He is no respecter of persons, and I am going to... I put so many walls up thinking, "Well, you know, you have to be perfect."God's not looking for perfection.

00:17:07.890 --> 00:17:26.377
He's just looking for "yes". Isaiah 6:6-8: "Then one of the seraphim flew to me with a burning coal he had taken from the altar with a pair of tongs.

00:17:26.378 --> 00:17:33.978
He touched my lips with it and said, 'See, this coal has touched your lips.

00:17:33.979 --> 00:17:47.800
Now your guilt is removed and your sins are forgiven.'Then I heard the Lord ask, 'Who should I send as a messenger to the people?

00:17:47.801 --> 00:17:57.932
Who will go for us?'I said, 'Here am I. Send me. Here am I. Send me.'"Do you know what?

00:17:57.933 --> 00:18:03.703
We don't have maybe an angel coming down and putting a coal of fire on our lips.

00:18:03.704 --> 00:18:09.954
We have the blood of Jesus. We take communion and we go before Him daily.

00:18:09.955 --> 00:18:14.416
I take communion. Smith Wigglesworth took communion all the time. John G.

00:18:14.417 --> 00:18:23.140
Lake took communion all the time, and William Seymour and those, and I practice what the elders did.

00:18:23.141 --> 00:18:28.879
I look at them, I say, "If they did it, I do it. If they read their Bible every 15 minutes, I'm going to find some scripture.

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:41.678
I'm going to find something to stir me up because we leak out."And we may not have an actual angel come down and put a coal on our lips, but we have the blood of Jesus that has made us whole.

00:18:41.679 --> 00:18:52.079
We have the blood, the ultimate sacrifice that said, "Hey, I have forgiven you."And you say, "Who?"He touched my lips.

00:18:52.080 --> 00:18:59.051
Jesus touched your lips. Jesus touched your lips with it and said, "See this coal.

00:18:59.052 --> 00:19:09.199
See this blood."His sacrifice has touched your lips. Now your guilt is removed and your sins are forgiven.

00:19:09.200 --> 00:19:15.369
Jesus washed away all your sins. Jesus paid the price for you to walk in victory.

00:19:15.370 --> 00:19:21.242
And just like the angel back then did that to him, we had Jesus do it for us.

00:19:21.243 --> 00:19:26.650
He was the ultimate sacrifice. He put it all on the altar. He did it all.

00:19:26.651 --> 00:19:35.695
His blood was enough, and I acknowledge what He did for me. I do this often in remembrance.

00:19:35.696 --> 00:19:44.072
"Jesus, I thank you for what you did for me."His blood was more than enough, and I just acknowledge it. "Thank you.

00:19:44.073 --> 00:19:51.275
Thank you, Lord, that you paid the price for me to walk in victory."See, the coal has touched your lips.

00:19:51.276 --> 00:20:09.918
Now, your guilt is removed and your sins are forgiven. Who can the Lord send in these last days? You're more than enough because of His blood.

00:20:09.919 --> 00:20:24.936
Then I heard the Lord ask—He's asking tonight—"Who should I send as a messenger to the people?"I heard it today. I was driving around and I went around ORU again.

00:20:24.937 --> 00:20:34.469
I drove around again, sat out there and said, "Who can I send, Brandon?"I was not going to do a broadcast tonight.

00:20:34.470 --> 00:20:43.439
He said, "I want you to do one for me, please."I said, "I will now."Okay.

00:20:43.440 --> 00:20:52.479
Then I heard the Lord asking, "Who should I send as a messenger to this people?

00:20:52.480 --> 00:21:07.132
Who will go for us?"I said, "Here am I. Send me."I was driving and I was almost home, and I was turning around.

00:21:07.133 --> 00:21:13.199
I was going down and I was getting my kids something to eat. And I said, "Lord, it's over there.

00:21:13.200 --> 00:21:29.359
I'm trying to not go through the traffic."He said, "It's not going to be convenient, everything I ask you to do."I said, "Okay."He said, "I want you to go over there, and I want you to sit, because you're thinking too small.

00:21:29.360 --> 00:21:33.460
I want you to sit in front of that Mabee Center because you're thinking too small.

00:21:33.461 --> 00:21:37.608
And remember the words that I've told you, that I'm bringing a revival to Tulsa.

00:21:37.609 --> 00:21:46.798
I'm going to bring a revival to the nations. You're thinking too small. You're thinking too poverty. You're thinking too little.

00:21:46.799 --> 00:22:19.669
Braden, look big."And I remember across the school that it says in that auditorium, "Make no little plans here."Oral Roberts had big on the inside of him, as I saw the big building and the medical center—they sold it now, but it was worth over $300 million, the building and all the stuff—and I was looking at all that he'd done whenever he was here, the campus, and I just sat there looking at it.

00:22:19.670 --> 00:22:28.959
And Diana and I... she goes, "Why are we here?"I said, "To get big on the inside of me, you got to get big on the inside of you.

00:22:28.960 --> 00:22:36.959
Start focusing on something other than your small world and realize that God wants us to reach the nations.

00:22:36.960 --> 00:22:46.088
Many, many people are dying and going to hell. And we limit ourselves in our own stinking thinking and think, 'Well, I'm not good enough.

00:22:46.089 --> 00:22:53.027
I have a past.'Who doesn't have a past? I'm talking to you. Who doesn't have a past?

00:22:53.028 --> 00:22:59.359
There's so many people that have a past. Your testimony is great.

00:22:59.360 --> 00:23:08.759
'Well, I did this. I got a divorce. I had an abortion. God can't use me.'But you're so mistaken.

00:23:08.760 --> 00:23:16.319
The blood is enough for you. The blood is enough for you tonight.

00:23:16.320 --> 00:23:23.430
There's no one that has too much sin in their life that God can't touch their lips with that blood, with that coal.

00:23:23.431 --> 00:23:35.279
He touched my lips with it and said, 'See, this coal has touched your lips.'The blood tonight, Jesus's sacrifice, touched your lips.

00:23:35.280 --> 00:24:05.519
Now your guilt is removed and your sins are forgiven. Then I heard the Lord ask, 'Whom should I send as a messenger?'I just believe it.

00:24:05.520 --> 00:24:12.639
We're in the last of the last days here. Jesus Christ is coming.

00:24:12.640 --> 00:24:18.393
We're in the last of the last days here, and Jesus Christ is coming, and it's time for you to be all in.

00:24:18.394 --> 00:24:23.940
As I sat and I looked at that Mabee Center and I saw again—do you see the fire on top of the building?

00:24:23.941 --> 00:24:34.178
Do you see the glory that's about to be poured out over Tulsa, over Victory across the street with Paul Daugherty, and the glory?

00:24:34.179 --> 00:24:39.240
And he said this would be overflow. And I saw the old hotel that's closed down now.

00:24:39.241 --> 00:24:45.135
It has weeds all on the beds; it's all run down. This hotel across the street from the Mabee Center.

00:24:45.136 --> 00:24:51.278
And I sat there and just looked, and I thought, 'What would it take?'Because they're going to need something for the people to stay.

00:24:51.279 --> 00:24:54.871
There are going to be 24-hour-a-day services, seven days a week.

00:24:54.872 --> 00:25:03.439
There has got to be some place for these people to stay. There's a Marriott down the road on 71st Street on Lewis.

00:25:03.440 --> 00:25:09.199
There's a Marriott, but that's not going to hold everybody.

00:25:09.200 --> 00:25:18.399
I thought, 'This is going to be something that we've never seen before.'I try to encourage you.

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:29.888
I remember whenever I was praying one night and I was interceding, and the Lord took me into the throne room, and I saw him sitting on his throne, and he came out.

00:25:29.889 --> 00:25:36.339
He was shielding himself because the light was so bright. I thought my eyes were going to burn out of my head.

00:25:36.340 --> 00:25:40.945
The vision, even in a vision, it was not natural. I wasn't really there.

00:25:40.946 --> 00:25:46.367
I think if I was really there, it would have killed me. That's how bright this was.

00:25:46.368 --> 00:25:54.092
But every single time, he has to shield himself. But it was so bright, it was so beautiful.

00:25:54.093 --> 00:26:06.391
He came out of it as a massive eye of fire. The fire was moving, and everything he said in the throne room, it became a seed.

00:26:06.392 --> 00:26:20.636
It was the size of a grain of a mustard seed. And the mustard seed grain, every word became alive, and they all joined together and started to form roots. They didn't die.

00:26:20.637 --> 00:26:43.793
His words became alive, and they formed all together, and they came as a seed, and the seed grew together, and the roots formed, and the sentences all lined up, and they all formed one massive, beautiful thing as they started drinking from a pool of water that was below.

00:26:43.794 --> 00:26:52.880
And it was ankle-deep, it was waist-deep, it was over, and I could see the water, and it was just pure as the eye could see.

00:26:52.881 --> 00:26:56.766
The water was as deep all the way at the beginning at the base of his throne.

00:26:56.767 --> 00:27:08.798
I could see this beautiful water. And he said, 'You must go down to the deep. You must go down to the deeper water.

00:27:08.799 --> 00:27:20.719
You used to abide there all the time, but over the course of time, you've gotten dry.'And I was looking at that water, and I said, 'Lord, how do I get back in that?

00:27:20.720 --> 00:27:31.156
The cares of this world pull you out; you become dry.'And I could see the water, and it was the most beautiful pools of water.

00:27:31.157 --> 00:27:39.199
It was all different levels. There's levels of the glory; there's levels of his presence.

